              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "23-V-51",
                "field_identifier": "NAT",
                "value": 0.9975
              },
              "free_text": [
                " 10 ppm standard solution of",
                "vanadium, and the  comparator isotope Mn-55 as also",
                "contained in a 10 ppm standard  solution of manganese.",
                "The certified concentration of manganese in  the",
                "manganese standard solution was 10.01 +/- 0.03 mg/g",
                "and that of  vanadium was 4.86 +/- 0.02 mg/g in the",
                "vanadium standard solution."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The extent of non-ideality of epithermal flux shape,",
                "alpha-factor at the sample irradiation position was",
                "experimentally determined to be 0.134 +/- 0.01 by",
                "dual monitor method using 197Au and 95Zr. The thermal",
                "neutron flux is (1.46+/-0.01)x10**4 n/cm**2/s and the",
                "epithermal neutron flux is",
                " (7.23+/-0.02)x10**2 n/cm**2/s."
              ]
            }
          ],
